---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <div class="bg-gray-950 py-20">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 prose prose-invert">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">How to Spot and Remove Tech Support Scams in 2026</h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">July 2026 • RigRescue Blog</p>

            <p>Tech support scams continue to be one of the most common threats to everyday computer users. Here's how to recognize them and what to do if you've been targeted.</p>

            <h2>Common Signs of a Tech Support Scam</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Unsolicited pop-up warnings claiming your computer is infected</li>
                <li>Calls from “Microsoft” or “Windows Support”</li>
                <li>Pressure to act immediately or your computer will be locked</li>
                <li>Requests for remote access to your PC</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>What to Do If You See a Scam</h2>
            <p>Do not call the number on the screen. Close the window or restart your computer. Then contact a trusted local or remote technician like RigRescue for a proper diagnostic. If you didn't call the number its VERY likely you are safe! If you did call the number and allow them on to the machine we can help! Most times its not more than the diagnostic cost as they rarely instal real viruses just software to allow them back onto the machine. That sort of software is quick and easy to remove!</p>

            <h2>How RigRescue Can Help</h2>
            <p>We specialize in remote virus/malware removal and scam cleanup. Our $50 diagnostic is credited toward the full repair, and we never start work without your approval.</p>

            <div class="text-center mt-12">
                <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg font-medium">
                    Get Scam Cleanup Help Today
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
